Spring AI 通过多个层面处理 Agent 观测（observability），包括指标监控、日志记录、工具使用分析、会话事件溯源和进度追踪。以下按文档逐一说明：

---

## 一、Micrometer 集成与 Actuator 指标（内置可观测性）

**[297aad4bbeac986ea2b37c857d66a55f:0009]**

> Observability is crucial in any enterprise application, and applications enhanced with generative AI are no exception. Spring AI offers built-in observability features, enabling seamless monitoring of your AI services' health and performance. This includes comprehensive metrics, tracing, and logging for end-to-end visibility into your generative AI application. This is not just for the chat model — it's for the entire stack, including the embedding model and the vector database.

> With Spring AI, you gain insights into critical metrics like token usage rate, which is essential for managing cost when interacting with models that charge based on the number of tokens processed. Additionally, you can monitor vector store latency, error rates, and even trace how requests flow through your AI-enhanced services.

**[c33ece843f91c7a78226c1d82fe20109:0010]**

具体配置：在 `application.properties` 中暴露 Actuator 端点：

```
management.endpoints.web.exposure.include=*
management.endpoint.health.show-details=always
```

重启后访问 `localhost:8080/actuator/metrics` 即可看到以 `gen_ai` 为前缀的指标，例如 `gen_ai.client.token.usage`。详细信息可通过 `localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/gen_ai.client.token.usage` 查看。

> The metrics integration is powered by the fabulous Micrometer project, which integrates with darn near every time series database under the sun, including Prometheus, Graphite, Netflix Atlas, DataDog, Dynatrace, etc. So, you could also have these metrics published to those TSDBs to help build out that all important single pane of glass experience for operations.

**[c33ece843f91c7a78226c1d82fe20109:0021]**

> All requests to an LLM have a cost — at least one of complexity, if not dollars and cents. As we explored earlier, the Spring Boot observability story is ideal here.

---

## 二、Advisor 机制：自定义日志记录

**[84a7c1fbee6b150bfcf7555afb536a11:0001]**

> At their core, Spring AI Advisors are components that intercept and potentially modify the flow of chat-completion requests and responses in your AI applications.

**[84a7c1fbee6b150bfcf7555afb536a11:0005]**

通过实现 `CallAroundAdvisor` 和 `StreamAroundAdvisor` 接口，可以创建自定义日志 Advisor，在请求处理前后记录交互细节：

```java
public class SimpleLoggerAdvisor implements CallAroundAdvisor, StreamAroundAdvisor {
    private static final Logger logger = LoggerFactory.getLogger(SimpleLoggerAdvisor.class);

    @Override
    public AdvisedResponse aroundCall(AdvisedRequest advisedRequest, CallAroundAdvisorChain chain) {
        logger.debug("BEFORE: {}", advisedRequest);
        AdvisedResponse advisedResponse = chain.nextAroundCall(advisedRequest);
        logger.debug("AFTER: {}", advisedResponse);
        return advisedResponse;
    }

    @Override
    public Flux<AdvisedResponse> aroundStream(AdvisedRequest advisedRequest, StreamAroundAdvisorChain chain) {
        logger.debug("BEFORE: {}", advisedRequest);
        Flux<AdvisedResponse> advisedResponses = chain.nextAroundStream(advisedRequest);
        return new MessageAggregator().aggregateAdvisedResponse(advisedResponses,
                advisedResponse -> logger.debug("AFTER: {}", advisedResponse));
    }
}
```

> This Advisor logs the request before it's processed and the response after it's received, providing valuable insights into the AI interaction process.

**[84a7c1fbee6b150bfcf7555afb536a11:0009]**

多个 Advisor 之间可通过共享的 `advise-context` 对象传递状态，构建更复杂的观测场景：

> Both the `AdvisedRequest` and the `AdvisedResponse` share an advise-context object. You can use the `advise-context` to share state between the advisors in the chain, and build more complex processing scenarios that involve multiple advisors.

---

## 三、Tool Argument Augmenter：工具使用分析

**[c773530a57cf430013f7d8e2695ea7f4:0003]**

Tool Argument Augmenter 动态扩展工具的 JSON Schema，注入额外字段（如 `innerThoughts`），在不修改工具本身的前提下捕获 LLM 的推理过程和元数据。

**[c773530a57cf430013f7d8e2695ea7f4:0015]**

通过定义 `ToolAnalytics` 记录结合分析工具使用模式：

```java
public record ToolAnalytics(
    @ToolParam(description = "Why did you choose this specific tool?", required = true)
    String toolSelectionReason,

    @ToolParam(description = "What result do you expect from this tool?", required = false)
    String expectedOutcome,

    @ToolParam(description = "User intent classification", required = true)
    String userIntent
) {}

Consumer<AugmentedArgumentEvent<ToolAnalytics>> analyticsProcessor = event -> {
    ToolAnalytics analytics = event.arguments();
    String toolName = event.toolDefinition().name();

    metricsCollector.recordToolSelection(
        toolName,
        analytics.userIntent(),
        analytics.toolSelectionReason()
    );

    if (analytics.expectedOutcome() != null) {
        // Compare expected vs actual outcomes for quality metrics
        outcomeTracker.recordExpectation(toolName, analytics.expectedOutcome());
    }
};
```

**[c773530a57cf430013f7d8e2695ea7f4:0013]**

该机制还可与 Advisor 链结合构建具备记忆的 Agent，并实现"对 LLM 决策过程的完整可观测性"：

> The partial document introduces a method for building intelligent AI agents with memory by combining a Tool Argument Augmenter with Spring AI's advisor chain. ... The main points covered include tool-level reasoning capture, conversation continuity through memory, full observability into LLM decision-making, and a note on advisor chain ordering.

---

## 四、Session API：事件溯源与 Recall 存储

**[b21473004eac5bc06d327bcf40015952:0002]**

Session API 以事件溯源方式记录所有会话事件，每个 `SessionEvent` 包含 UUID、sessionId、timestamp、可选的 branch 标签（用于多 Agent 层级）以及框架标记（如 METADATA_SYNTHETIC）。

**[b21473004eac5bc06d327bcf40015952:0009]**

Recall Storage 确保即使 compaction 从活跃 prompt 中移除了旧事件，完整的 verbatim 事件日志仍然持久保留并可通过关键词搜索：

> `SessionEventTools` implements the MemGPT *Recall Storage* pattern: the full verbatim event log is always retained and searchable by keyword, even after compaction has pruned it from the prompt.

> The `conversation_search` tool is auto-discovered by Spring AI. When the model needs to recall a prior exchange it calls the tool with a keyword and an optional `page` index; results come back as chronologically ordered JSON.

**[b21473004eac5bc06d327bcf40015952:0008]**

多 Agent 分支隔离通过 `SessionEvent` 中的 dot-separated branch path 实现，`EventFilter.forBranch()` 配合 `SessionMemoryAdvisor` 自动隔离各 Agent 的可见范围，使每个子 Agent 只能看到自身分支和祖先节点。

---

## 五、TodoWriteTool：事件驱动进度追踪

**[abbbabf9779d3bbd40279c749e155ed0:0006]**

TodoWriteTool 发布 Spring `ApplicationEvent`，应用可监听这些事件实现实时 UI 更新：

> The tool publishes events that your application can use to update UIs in real-time.

通过注入 `ApplicationEventPublisher` 并在 `todoEventHandler` 中发布自定义事件（如 `TodoUpdateEvent`），再通过 `@EventListener` 监听器实时追踪任务完成进度（如 completed/total 比例）。

---

## 小结

Spring AI 对 Agent 观测的处理覆盖了从基础设施层到业务逻辑层的完整链路：

| 层面 | 机制 | 核心能力 |
|------|------|----------|
| 基础设施指标 | Micrometer + Actuator | Token 用量、向量库延迟、错误率，可接入 Prometheus/DataDog 等 |
| 请求拦截日志 | Advisor 链 | 请求前/后日志、跨 Advisor 状态共享 |
| 工具调用分析 | Tool Argument Augmenter | 捕获推理过程、工具选择理由、预期结果、用户意图 |
| 会话事件溯源 | Session API | 完整事件日志、关键词搜索、多 Agent 分支隔离 |
| 任务进度追踪 | TodoWriteTool 事件 | 实时进度事件发布与 UI 更新 |

